channel.title: Flog It!
channel.desc: Paul Martin presents from Muncaster Castle in Cumbria. Experts Caroline Hawley and James Lewis choose items to take to auction. James is drawn to a collection of WWI memorabilia and Caroline finds an exciting collection of postcards. Plus, Paul meets an artist whose work has led him back in time to the ancient art of relief printing.
